      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on the same device geometry (FDA generic centrifugal pump) under overlapping operating conditions with the intended simulation use.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry using the same blood analog fluid (glycerol-water) and operating envelope as the intended CPB simulations. Geometric and operational relevance confirmed."
