    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements with documented justification. CFD model of FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device application. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts and the assessment team finds the evidence body adequate for the stated decision.",
